		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="As Lae'zel Avatar, go to act 1b. &#xD;&#xA;Go the security office and accept or refuse Vlaakith's mission. &#xD;&#xA;Insert the Artefact into the planecaster object&#xD;&#xA;Once in the astral prison, follow the wisp to its final destination and talk to it." />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="623" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Avatar Lae'zel meets Daisy in person for the first time. Daisy will invite the player to kill them, knowing that Vlaakith has ordered the player to do so. The player will be able to ask Daisy about the astral prison, the Absolute, and why the gith are after them," />
